Package: EasySentiment
Type: Package
Title: A package for easy and quick sentiment analysis.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Diego", "Ford", email = "diegoford0815@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is a tool for conducting sentiment analysis quickly and easily.
    It will provide tools for measuring sentiments using the various sentiment dictionaries.
    All you need to feed into it is a vector of string you would like analyzed.
    There will be tools for summary statistics, creating TDMs or DTMs and different visualizations.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
